36:13.590 --> 36:25.228
hospital, but not up to really the efficiency you 
expect someone to do. And there's no question that

36:25.529 --> 36:37.247
affected my career from then on because I always 
had this problem that you lift anything or run,

36:25.529 --> 36:37.247
pain comes back, still does. Of course, I've 
learned now there's no reason for exertion. Well,

36:42.234 --> 36:46.781
John, we'll get back to the military command 
center. And you were telling me about the

36:46.801 --> 36:50.507
functions and duties there. Right. If you 
visualize all of these people and with their

36:51.671 --> 37:19.043
knowledge and their accessibility to, because 
they themselves continually got updated, I don't

36:51.671 --> 37:19.043
mean every second, but they were sure that from 
their sources, and the Army has an operations

36:51.671 --> 37:19.043
center, the Navy does, and the Air Force, but this 
was, and we were all tied into them, so we were fed

36:51.671 --> 37:19.043
information from everyone. The key part, 
however, to the facility was the communication we

37:20.120 --> 37:26.629
had. And it was off to the side. And we could speak 
directly to any command element in the world where

37:30.855 --> 37:45.455
we had U.S. And each day we would test that command. 
We'd actually come home with a conference call,

37:45.515 --> 37:49.941
the flag officer. would go in in the communication 
because the outside was local communications

37:50.883 --> 37:56.289
type of thing. But this was the

37:56.369 --> 38:01.556
powerful communication. And they didn't even, 
communication even had a capability. If you had a

38:04.739 --> 38:09.465
weak signal, they could raise the volume on that 
signal. Would it be by satellite? Yeah, they used

38:12.268 --> 38:15.672
satellite, the whole range of communication. And 
we also have an airborne command post, and a Navy

38:21.832 --> 38:28.180
command post. So we would bring them in this 
community check, communication check with the

38:29.021 --> 38:33.847
others.

38:37.511 --> 38:38.693
We'd go to use the . I'll say every place that we had a 
command. I don't mean down a lower level, but we had

38:42.217 --> 38:45.121
the capability of doing that. For example, we had a

38:52.308 --> 39:05.648
The bomb says, let's see, we had

38:52.308 --> 39:05.648
a month or two which there was no bombing in North 
Vietnam. But the situation was such that the

39:08.151 --> 39:12.838
decision had been made to resume bombing.

39:17.085 --> 39:20.830
Secretary of State called, I happened to be on 
duty, And he says, this is very important. I want to

39:24.721 --> 39:32.450
know when the first bomb drops in the resumption of 
bombing in North Vietnam. Now, he pointed out this

39:33.291 --> 39:39.117
is important because we have pre-positioned 
messages at all of our embassies in the world. And I

39:40.638 --> 39:48.006
don't want to prematurely release this for 
weather conditions or reason, you know, that we

39:40.638 --> 39:48.006
really can't execute the mission. Can you let me 
know immediately? And I said, yes, sir. So all we

39:52.512 --> 40:01.940
did was go through the sink back with this powerful 
communication, went on into the carriers were

39:52.512 --> 40:01.940
going to make the first strike. To them, I talked to 
the, it wasn't a captain, it was an officer on, I

40:02.621 --> 40:19.656
guess a man in their community, their duty officer 
on the carrier, and explained what our situation

40:02.621 --> 40:19.656
was and can you let me know when the first bomb is 
dropped. No abortion or anything like that the

40:25.892 --> 40:27.874
first time. He said, absolutely. He says, I'll 
patch in right now to the flight commander. And you

40:35.842 --> 40:40.527
will hear him tell me when he has dropped, when the 
bomb's away. So here I am monitoring with the clock

40:42.069 --> 40:44.631
ticking along. So pretty soon you heard. Of 
course, I was a little bit weaker because he was

40:46.033 --> 40:49.356
coming from the radio. And he says, bombs away. So 
immediately it called up the State Department. It

40:54.769 --> 40:59.036
was just a matter of, well, almost 
simultaneously. We had in Washington the word.

41:01.601 --> 41:04.445
Now you don't like to do that because you tie up a lot 
of communication. You like to deal only with the

41:04.986 --> 41:08.532
headquarters rather than go on down. But you just 
heard the fighter pilot just say, bombs away.

41:13.340 --> 41:14.382
Yeah, he gave a... The word, it might have been 
other words at that time, but anyway, whatever he

41:15.138 --> 41:21.426
said, the indication. Right at that second, you 
got on the phone and called the State Department.

41:24.830 --> 41:25.331
Yeah, exactly. So the Secretary of State knew 
about that almost simultaneously, just a few

41:25.351 --> 41:32.980
minutes. That's just an example of the 
communication, how it worked. That's fantastic.

41:36.324 --> 41:37.966
Now, you get involved with a lot of things.

41:40.870 --> 41:44.014
On the desk of the flag officer is a red telephone. 
That's directly to the president from the White

41:45.513 --> 41:48.837
House. And whenever that red light comes on, 
flashes, it actually flashes. Of course, you also

41:56.046 --> 41:57.788
hear a signal. When you pick that up, there's no 
secretary on there. It's the president himself.

42:03.675 --> 42:04.656
And usually he calls. This was LBJ. He'd call about 
2 or 3 o'clock in the morning. Some said perhaps he

42:11.144 --> 42:14.828
had a bladder problem, but he slept very little. 
And he had, he monitored all of television, CBS,

42:15.854 --> 42:26.625
NBC, all of them at the same time, plus radio. And if 
a news flash came over about a strike

42:26.645 --> 42:42.520
in Vietnam, say they had heavy casualties, 
several planes were lost, these are just news

42:26.645 --> 42:42.520
reports, he'd be on that line asking He wanted an 
update, because I just heard that. Can you tell me

42:45.261 --> 42:47.863
about it? Well, while you're talking, of course, 
we have all the information we have that my

42:47.883 --> 43:00.357
assistant, who's also, he's on the line, and he 
signals the individual whose area we're talking

42:47.883 --> 43:00.357
about. Of course, it's always Vietnam. So he ran up 
with a map, put it up in front, and he was handing

43:02.299 --> 43:10.768
information while we were talking to the 
president, trying to answer his questions. Of

43:11.339 --> 43:17.786
course, oftentimes we didn't have it, so we just 
had to tell you, well, Mr. President, we don't have

43:11.339 --> 43:17.786
an update on that. I'll notify your situation room 
just as soon as we have it. And he said, all right,

43:23.171 --> 43:25.133
thank you. White House has a situation room, too, 
where they monitor these things. And often he

43:32.020 --> 43:37.566
called them, but he finally got word that they 
didn't know because they'd have to get the

43:32.020 --> 43:37.566
information from us. So they, too, were always 
asking us, please update us on this, because they

43:38.423 --> 43:43.710
anticipated he might come. His son-in-law was up 
near Khe Sanh.

43:52.200 --> 43:54.703
And he was very anxious about a situation up there. 
He didn't say, I don't wonder if my son-in-law was

43:54.803 --> 43:56.846
there. Obviously, what was happening? I 
shouldn't even say that, because he was

43:58.888 --> 44:01.592
interested in every single thing. It really hurt 
him to have a report that a pilot had been lost. It

44:06.798 --> 44:08.120
really hurt LBJ. Yeah. He wanted to say any chance 
to find that pilot. Of course, you can't answer

44:13.516 --> 44:15.418
that, I mean, here. And you don't go back like I've 
said and try to find out the unit. Sure. But it's a

44:20.925 --> 44:22.407
normal routine.

44:25.831 --> 44:32.319
But when his son-in-law was over in Vietnam, he was 
on the phone more often asking about the area? No,

44:32.340 --> 44:33.881
he seemed to call now. While I was on duty, I guess he 
called me four times. And I guess the other flag

44:39.308 --> 44:42.993
also on duty, probably about the same area. That's 
over a period of a year that I was there. So he didn't

44:45.075 --> 44:46.357
call every night. But it was always, the call was 
generated by something that he had just seen or

44:46.938 --> 44:56.330
heard on the radio or television, particularly at 
night. And some said it wasn't a bladder problem,

44:57.091 --> 45:01.276
but he just couldn't sleep. Didn't only need two or 
three hours of sleep. And he wanted to talk to

45:05.762 --> 45:07.324
somebody. Sometimes in the daytime, they'd say, 
get me that general on the phone. And they meant

45:13.377 --> 45:17.824
that general in the National Military Command 
Center. But he sure took a personal interest and

45:17.844 --> 45:22.752
suffered with all those guys, so they can't. Of 
course, he was under great pressure to recall, you

45:22.772 --> 45:29.382
know, yelling at him, LBJ, how many did you kill 
today? Another example of a domestic problem that

